Package org.chronos.chronodb.api.builder.database

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ChronoDBBaseBuilder
    This is the starter interface for building a ChronoDB interface in a fluent API.
    ChronoDBChunkedBuilder  
    ChronoDBFinalizableBuilder<SELF extends ChronoDBFinalizableBuilder<?>>
    A builder for instances of ChronoDB.
    ChronoDBInMemoryBuilder
    A builder for in-memory instances of ChronoDB.
    ChronoDBJdbcBuilder
    A builder for instances of ChronoDB which store their data in a JDBC-compatible relational database.
    ChronoDBMapDBBuilder
    A builder for creating instances of ChronoDB that rely on MapDB as backend.
    ChronoDBPropertyFileBuilder
    A builder for all kinds of instances of ChronoDB, based on a *.properties file.
    ChronoDBTuplBuilder
    A builder for creating instances of ChronoDB that rely on TUPL as backend.
